Extends npm cache add to support direct local tarball injection,
using the syntax <package-spec>|<path/to.tgz>.

Resolves and validates the local tarball path, streams the tarball into cacache,
stores both normal cache entry and a SHA-1-addressed variant for legacy compat.

For https:// specs, also populates request-cache metadata,
so the cached tarball behaves like a fetched artifact.

